videos.description: Jake Browning pass complete to John Ross for 51 yds to the OrgSt 19 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: 51- Yard Pass to keep the Huskies opening drive alive

videos.description: Aaron Fuller is left wide open in the end zone for Jake Browning to find with an easy 19 yards touchdown pass putting Washington up early on Oregon State 7-0.
videos.headline: Washington jumps out early with 19-yard TD

videos.description: Jake Browning to John Ross on the flea flicker for 44 yards.
videos.headline: Husky Trickeration for 44 yards

videos.description: Jake Browning run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: Browning gets the 2nd Husky TD on the ground.

videos.description: Jake Browning hits Dante Pettis with a 23-yard touchdown to give Washington a 21-0 lead over Oregon State.
videos.headline: Browning scores his third TD of the game

videos.description: Myles Gaskin run for 9 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Myles Gaskin spins and tumbles to put Washington up 28

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass intercepted Darren Gardenhire return for 25 yds to the Wash 45
videos.headline: Huskies pick the ball off before halftime

videos.description: Jake Browning throws his third passing touchdown, and fourth total touchdown of the game, to Dante Pettis to give Washington a 38-3 lead over Oregon State.
videos.headline: Browning tosses third passing touchdown of the game

videos.description: Victor Bolden Jr. run for 75 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Victor Bolden 75-Yard TD gives Oregon State 1st TD of the game

videos.description: Tim Cook run for 9 yds for a TD (Garrett Owens KICK)
videos.headline: Tim Cook 9-yard TD

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass intercepted Austin Joyner return for no gain to the Wash 31
videos.headline: Austin Joyner with an improbable interception
